    "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Villages™</strong> is a game that combines interesting mechanics from many other sandbox games. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It aims to let People face a variety of gameplay and scenario by conducting a few basic rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749820/extras/1880ca621386536666ea8a99ee2f4686.avif?t=1745372892\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KEY FEATURES</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Economy, the game's world will have limited resources, so ones will not get the same resources and amount. <br> People will then form an economy by using the trading system in the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can make a product with different tiers, from hand-crafted to factory-made. <br> Each tier varies in cost and benefit and makes it dynamic to the whole economy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construction differs from a traditional sandbox game. Villages™ lets you construct a building as if in real life by using construction sites, tools, and vehicles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill-Based, People can choose their skill to advance, but with limited skill points.  <br>So you must balance your skill branches and benefit from them. <br> Everyone will depend on other People's abilities and form their society.</p></li></ul>",
    "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Villages™</strong> is a game that combines interesting mechanics from many other sandbox games. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It aims to let People face a variety of gameplay and scenario by conducting a few basic rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749820/extras/1880ca621386536666ea8a99ee2f4686.avif?t=1745372892\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KEY FEATURES</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Economy, the game's world will have limited resources, so ones will not get the same resources and amount. <br> People will then form an economy by using the trading system in the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can make a product with different tiers, from hand-crafted to factory-made. <br> Each tier varies in cost and benefit and makes it dynamic to the whole economy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construction differs from a traditional sandbox game. Villages™ lets you construct a building as if in real life by using construction sites, tools, and vehicles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill-Based, People can choose their skill to advance, but with limited skill points.  <br>So you must balance your skill branches and benefit from them. <br> Everyone will depend on other People's abilities and form their society.</p></li></ul>",
